text: Trayan Dimitrov (; born 2 February 1947) is a Bulgarian fencer. He competed in the individual sabre event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bulgaria Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Bulgarian sabre fencers
